title: 2016 City Manager's Proposed Budget Presentation (City of Newburgh, NY)
text: (Source: City of Newburgh, NY) On Tuesday, October 13, 2015 City Manager Michael G. Ciaravino presented the proposed 2016 budget to the City Council.
